[I] Tool to create Python bindings for C and C++

[T] SIP is a tool that makes it very easy to create Python bindings
[T] for C and C++ libraries. It was originally developed to create
[T] PyQt, the Python bindings for the Qt toolkit, but can be used to
[T] create bindings for any C or C++ library.

[U] http://www.riverbankcomputing.co.uk/sip/

[A] Riverbank Computing Ltd. <http://www.riverbankcomputing.co.uk>
